page.title: 07EMPLOYMENT
page.content: Precision Engineering Garage servicing and petrol sales Village Shops Public Houses and Restaurants Tourism Goat Husbandry Boarding Kennels Under the category of Precision Engineering we note with interest a small busines concern employing only one person but involved with small components for a variety of uses such as life-saving equipment hydraulic system for sliding doors assembly of parts for electrical distributors,also additional buildings in this small complex were let to three other one man business ventures such as Paint Spraying General Motor Mechanics and General Motor Repairers
